572
01:03:12.200 --> 01:03:13.560
They're trying to get votes.

573
01:03:14.280 --> 01:03:17.640
Otherwise, their whole idea doesn't go anywhere.

574
01:03:17.640 --> 01:03:40.620
And so our whole, everything about our political discourse is very like fast food advertising and fast food food, which is instant gratification, nice stuff that tastes yummy, at least for a while, and stuff that's actually not very good for you.

575
01:03:40.620 --> 01:03:41.900
