576
01:03:41.960 --> 01:03:43.780
You're a bit of a heart attack.

577
01:03:43.780 --> 01:03:45.220
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, that's right.

578
01:03:45.220 --> 01:03:52.000
So if I say, I mean, there are lots of things, there are lots of, and I was also talking about political correctness.

579
01:03:52.000 --> 01:04:00.720
There are a whole range of things that you can't say because they give an opportunity to an opponent to misrepresent you, okay?

580
01:04:00.720 --> 01:04:04.300
So if I said, let me just say something that's unacceptable.

581
01:04:04.300 --> 01:04:27.200
If I said, if I was advising a 14 year old girl going out on the town to discos on Friday night, if I said she might like to consider not dressing too provocatively because it might make her more likely to encounter violence, it's easy.

582
01:04:27.200 --> 01:04:28.680
