597
01:05:19.600 --> 01:05:20.580
Yeah.

598
01:05:20.580 --> 01:05:25.800
This is probably ties into why politicians' speech are so stereotypical.

599
01:05:25.800 --> 01:05:26.480
Of course it is.

600
01:05:26.480 --> 01:05:28.080
