602
01:05:34.600 --> 01:05:42.780
And battle-hardened language is language without color, without much commitment, which is, it's fast food language.

603
01:05:43.420 --> 01:05:45.260
This is a great hamburger.

604
01:05:46.140 --> 01:05:48.740
