701
01:14:36.220 --> 01:14:37.380
The big red bus.

702
01:14:37.380 --> 01:14:38.680
The big red bus.

703
01:14:38.680 --> 01:14:45.540
So that was clever campaigning, was highly misleading, and they managed to get out of the line 5248.

704
01:14:45.540 --> 01:14:47.300
