707
01:14:54.800 --> 01:14:57.780
That's no way to build political legitimacy.

708
01:14:57.780 --> 01:15:05.700
And they, I have very little doubt that they, if the EU survives, because the EU is nothing to get too excited about.

709
01:15:05.700 --> 01:15:10.500
I mean, it's a pretty awful organization in certain respects, and it may disintegrate.

710
01:15:10.500 --> 01:15:14.880
If the EU survives, Britain will be backing within 20 years.

711
01:15:14.880 --> 01:15:20.040
