740
01:18:18.640 --> 01:18:37.280
I hope you learned a few new things about ancient Athens, especially on the concept of Isagoria and how this concept of equality of speech is a feature of citizen juries, as well as the context it has as a potential pathway to our current electoral and representative method of governance around the modern world.

741
01:18:38.480 --> 01:18:42.020
